> `minimize: || A_i - I_i ||`

### 3. Regenerative Dividend Disparity Function (RDDF)
**Objective:** Align dividends with regenerative contribution.
> `maximize: R_i âˆ âˆ‚B/âˆ‚t_i`

### 4. Resilience Parity Function (RPF)
